com.vmware.nsx.dhcp.servers

Class ServersFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vmware.nsx.dhcp.servers.ServersFactory

  • public class ServersFactory
extends Object
    ServersFactory is responsible for creating instances of services contained inside the com.vmware.nsx.dhcp.servers package and also has the subpackages reference to access respective subpackage services.
